| Streamlit | Apache 2.0 | [streamlit.io](https://streamlit.io/) |
| Pydantic | MIT | [docs.pydantic.dev](https://docs.pydantic.dev/) |
| Pandas | BSD 3-Clause | [pandas.pydata.org](https://pandas.pydata.org/) |
